title: Long shot but looking to trade up for WaJo, Mathewson or Cy Young

posts.post_title: Long shot but looking to trade up for WaJo, Mathewson or Cy Young
posts.post_content:
Looking to trade a few or all of these for a nice Walter Johnson, Christy Mathewson or Cy Young.

Depending on the amount of cards I’m giving up, I would give 10-20% more in value to trade up.
